    "agendaChanges": "Item 10.1 (Discussion of Districtwide Solar Phase 2 Financial Study) was pulled from the agenda and deferred to a future meeting. Item 9.3 (Approval of Proposal for Intercom Buzzers at Hawes School with Atlas Pellizzari) was moved from Bond Program Consent Items to a standalone action item for individual discussion and vote. The closed session and report out were handled before the formal regular session agenda. The study session preceded the regular session as posted.",
